Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That email was the last I heard from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaori says she hasn't been able to reach her since yesterday either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yeah, sure. I'll contact you right away if anything comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So she didn't go back to her parents' place either?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Any chance she could be playing some kind of prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She jokes around sometimes, but she wouldn't do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess actually going there to check it out is our best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drag you along with me on your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I mixing personal and official business?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right as long as Gino doesn't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this friend of yours often visit places like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,More than a little. This has to be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am? By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recall doing anything to make any enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you do realize you're a detective, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving me that too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll go check it out. Just stay there and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this is really a trap, you'll be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want you to stay put. If we both get taken out, who's gonna call for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we call for backup right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel it's necessary, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, give me permission to carry arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tsunemori Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By my authority as an Inspector, I request permission for an Enforcer to carry arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Voiceprint and ID confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Level 2 equipment usage is granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the navigation to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the location map, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The data is old, but it's still usable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you see anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the back, it's just a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Wait... What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector, what happened? Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reading you loud and clear. Please keep going.{inb4 not her}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an abandoned subway line. Please check the train cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami! Can you hear me?! Come in!{yep}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an abandoned subway line. Please check the train cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm a detective with the Public Safety Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Funahara Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of Tsunemori Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Akane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of her colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. The basement is submerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,From the smell, it's gotta be polluted water mixed with liquid waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If something like that gets poured on you, you'll be in for a world of hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kougami definitely kept going past that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, he went back even further, seemingly through the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a problem with the navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The issue might not be with the hardware, but rather with the software.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this area has been repeatedly redeveloped,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd never know if the map data available matches the actual layout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one who got deceived here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Tsunemori?{bishounen full strength goddamn}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami left your supervision and now his whereabouts are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole situation might have been a setup for him to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... missy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose we trust the navigator instead of the map data.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know which direction Kougami was headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the signal show any strange movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, he suddenly started moving in a straight line, really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! He must have ended up in some kind of vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a subway line around here that runs in a north-south direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The subway Ginza Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was shut down sixty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you weren't the one who sent Tsunemori Akane that email?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone captured you and brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.{useless}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I got home late from work, so I took a bath and went straight to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, I was already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you were used as bait to lure Inspector Tsunemori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...subway line. Please investigate the train cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an abandoned subway line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane's voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's well made, but it's a fake created from voice samples.{akane is hatsune miku, you heard it here first}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew all along that she wouldn't be the one to come to the basement, but someone else instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Their target isn't Tsunemori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this means they want us to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. They're jamming all communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like they want to isolate us at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They want us to go in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Having to dance to this guy's tune kinda pisses me off, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like we have much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has gone to plan so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they're quick on the uptake too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The smarter the prey, the more enjoyable the hunt becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be a worthwhile game to watch from the bleachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take part in the hunt for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My interest lies in what will transpire during this hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'd be best for me to observe things as a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chemical lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't the flashlight be better?{not if you're going to a rave}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you carry a light source in the dark, you might as well paint a target on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can also use these to mark where we've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So Akane's job is really that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been especially bad lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've taken her concerns more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she does work at the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't discuss the details of her work with civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she doing okay at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She has...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...faith, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She intuitively understands what it means to be a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think what this society really needs is more people like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She was different even when we were in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the trouble was, once she intervened, it got resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if those with the clearest Psycho-Pass Hues are always people like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, could you be that subordinate that she doesn't know what to do with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how she talks about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even their traps are old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They've certainly got interesting tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A little to the right of the floor you just checked...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same bag we saw earlier!{herpderp lemme run into a trap brb}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I just saw someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Now I know what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to entertain themselves with some fox hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those drones are hunting dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When the prey gets frightened and runs, the hunter finishes it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves us as the poor foxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic. Don't get scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down and look for a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The more we panic, the more we play right into their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the bag you picked up earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a portable transponder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can communicate with this, even through their signal interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We can call for help?!{this bitch.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's missing the battery and antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll distract them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no chance with two hunting dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to bring at least one of them down,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,or they'll surround us, and that'll be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kougami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed one of them. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need now is the antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be a fox, but even foxes have sharp teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe he's really a member of the wolf family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima... Did you add some plot of your own to this game without my knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When a man faces fear, his soul is tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What he was born to seek, and what he was born to achieve...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,His true nature will become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just that Kougami guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interested in you too, Mr. Senguji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll face an unforeseen situation. An unexpected turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the wake of those, you too will face your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's the thrill and excitement you've been seeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I must say I don't really mind that habit you have of looking down on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kougami Shinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you understand the meaning of this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scary when you're quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They lured in Tsunemori, using you as bait,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but they knew it was actually me who'd go look for you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They factored all that in when setting up this hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you who they want to play with, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just... Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just someone who got dragged into this, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Your role in this should've been over after that email was sent at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did they put you on the subway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was to make it harder for you to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm holding you back like this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wasn't here, you'd find it much easier to escape, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Do what you wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This fox hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is not just a one-sided game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hinting that I've got a chance, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I'm being tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet that whether I abandon you or not
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is also one of the keys to winning this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take off your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Wh-What're you thinking about? Here, of all places!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you totally lost it or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna survive, just do what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe a perv like you is with the Bureau!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Whaddaya think you're looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you usually wear matching underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your underwear too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The last item needed to beat the game was hidden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the antenna for the transponder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some pretty heavy interference in this area, though the range is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the source of the interference?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from the southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But based on the map, there shouldn't be anything in that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. We'll set up a relay base here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't trust the map data.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Check every single gap thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the moment you see Kougami, shoot him with the Dominator.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be time for questions later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still don't know for sure if he ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sibyl System will make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If he didn't do anything wrong, his Crime Coefficient will be the same as before,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the gun's Paralyzer mode will settle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If he really wanted to run, the Eliminator mode will wipe him out without mercy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool the cymatic scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll show Kougami's real intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that it's okay to just kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be his friend, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If he ends up dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Tsunemori, it will be because of you and your poor supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd kept Kougami under control, none of this would have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about someone dying as a result of your own incompetence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you stop right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a little too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Kougami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can detect my location, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've got a Code 108 currently in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Send in reinforcements immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I repeat. A Code 108 is currently in progress. Send in reinforcements immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Send all the Drones we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know what path to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have them strike out randomly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure at least one Drone reaches him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:46.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,2200)\blur1}It seems all fairy tales {\alpha&HFF&}are dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.47,0:21:50.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,900)\blur1\alpha&HFF&}It seems {\alpha&H00&}all fairy tales are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:55.54,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}In a hospital ward of brick stones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:22:00.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}my voice is too coarse to sing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:05.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Outside in the foggy haze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:11.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}a red moon glows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:16.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:22.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Do not avert your gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Behind black bars
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.39,0:22:29.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I wish there were a punishment for evil
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.51,0:22:34.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Always I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:37.25,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Now, grant us justice
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.05,0:22:39.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}before chaos takes us all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:44.04,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Pay the price of fate and let us go together,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.72,0:22:49.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,500)\blur1}nameless beasts
